{"tid":1441240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下次班狗又發癲亂捉人不如直接打佢老母啦","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:00:56.000Z","uid":207202,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1efd333a2221aaab877388430c94513148276195","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"通常呢d時候都會有勁多人圍住幾隻狗<br />\n我地人多佢地人少<br />\n點解唔直接打佢老母<br />\n救返比人亂捉既人先<br />\n<br />\n當然，都要睇返人群外冇冇狗先得"},{"pid":"cc5722ad09644e16468117509a73fc17aace829a","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"34a4ea077cc90528d8083e24d6e03bc95e99ce4e","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ba53e0707e5736ec1b8e91ab6b9e3d2b31734241","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dfd16005f9a40de5ba1d5a7bb63bfcddb0af5d5d","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"13e4e8048f9e6601aa46b29f18a7938848131345","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"016fb45a883c2602e46fd4510d6ae8b3f59adcd9","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e0f0c6151a27bd534c0d33a8ed91865c22adbaca","tid":1441240,"uid":105605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:05.000Z","msg":"有機會"},{"pid":"02c015dc6a4158c493a279ec55972944e215daac","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d15721b70e3f53b9e2cf295d613f7a5bf820c0dd","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3c8f314956a07d514dedfe7c3df401bdf0c8441f","tid":1441240,"uid":73358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"780df844f1a5f30bd7a35bfb1a320f529fa3fcca","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d795cf65c0786f2e373e75556ee14227dac1dd","tid":1441240,"uid":127735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"通常要比記者係最前影，你呢個做法好兩極<br />\n救到是好，救唔到就大獲"},{"pid":"1730df453152dbf18ac1fc324db2af214ca0a84a","tid":1441240,"uid":285413,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家行動小心</strong></span></span>。<br />\n中共而家係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">黑白兩道</span></strong></span>落嚟打9大家<br />\n<br />\n大陸武警混入警隊 - 馮睎乾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435730</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗好耐，好多巴絲&amp;我都親身識家人的朋友係國安或知道哩件事，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>而家香港係多咗一倍警力</strong></span></span>，畀啲狗輪流休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫你整理少少證據<br />\n-家人識人落嚟香港做國安<br />\n-大埔講普通話&quot;同志，這邊&quot;<br />\n-有條差佬衝，唔聽白衫呀sir指揮亂衝<br />\n-唔戴委任證(因為佢哋冇)，所以索性全部人陪佢都唔戴<br />\n-有記者影到前線武裝警戴眼鏡唔戴con,話香港警察唔畀咁著(自行睇返上面條link)<br />\n-裝備錯搭，左輪手槍呀，嚴重槍械全部出動<br />\n-唔識警例<br />\n-突然大量人手<br />\netc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以其實等同暗出兵，如果大陸咁驚外國話佢出解放軍，我哋可以整段片(配不同語言字幕)再發送多國報紙話:<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其實解放軍已出</strong></span></span>&quot;<br />\n然後圖文並茂列出證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等到有更具體明顯證據時，例如:白警流出國安來港的文件，到時直情可落報紙廣告，國際譴責。"},{"pid":"08aecbbc3074aeea26ebeafb95853816eec0c2d7","tid":1441240,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"其實環境安全點解唔得<br />\n一人一棍打落去佢地點會仲捉<br />\n<br />\n但前提係 d狗冇支援"},{"pid":"7c5a159541b3ab8dded6dd5b4ad327ec2938cdbd","tid":1441240,"uid":116723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 評錯"},{"pid":"94d15e66bf75be750f38044cf0235cd6f42a2748","tid":1441240,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46274abab3a9bc9d5975f89c21922ee695ed61a","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80d795cf65c0786f2e373e75556ee14227dac1dd","tid":1441240,"uid":127735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"通常要比記者係最前影，你呢個做法好兩極<br />\n救到是好，救唔到就大獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"所以就係要睇隔離多唔多狗<br />\n小貓兩三隻就救左人先<br />\n比人亂捉個d有好多都係女仔，又唔知發生咩事<br />\n比人捉到狗竇好撚慘"},{"pid":"dbb4ebe6bd6c4e91272d4b4fa3dbfcfeb68b6808","tid":1441240,"uid":176392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"要係10秒內大家有共識"},{"pid":"0259e7af506de48e083cb4c0fdb078d22fef61a5","tid":1441240,"uid":207202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb4ebe6bd6c4e91272d4b4fa3dbfcfeb68b6808","tid":1441240,"uid":176392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"要係10秒內大家有共識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"通常有人帶頭其他人就會跟<br />\n除非有左膠在場啦"},{"pid":"802